{"tid":1739621,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《華郵》連續兩天頭版報道理大攻防戰 刊示威者突圍照","createTime":"2019-11-19T15:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T16:25:04.000Z","uid":135077,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa9b71b8707f028cf8bc726933b836eb4c60f55","tid":1739621,"uid":135077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:55:17.000Z","msg":"香港警方周日起包圍理工大學備受國際社會關注，美國《華盛頓郵報》繼周一後，連續兩天頭版報道理大「攻防戰」，周二在頭版及A26全版報道理大及香港示威的發展，並刊出了示威者在理大游繩突圍逃生的照片。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，理工大學被包圍後，不少示威者周一在九龍一帶增援，希望拉開警方的防線，讓受困的示威者有機會突圍，一些被困的示威者則成功透過游繩突圍逃生，並由電單車接走。《華郵》在頭版刊出由法新社拍下的照片，見到一名示威者正嘗試從天橋游繩離開理大。<br />\n《華郵》的記者在理大附近，訪問了一名懷疑是被困者的媽媽，她表示多日來不見了自己的兒子，「我不知道我的兒子是否在這裏。香港政府去了哪裏？我們的特首去了哪裏？防暴警察這樣包圍他們，是否只想讓我們的孩子死去？」<br />\n<br />\n美國《華盛頓郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191119/60286868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60286868&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=53eb072a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60286868&h=3c447e6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191119/60286868</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連Washington Post都出手同我地我助攻 要令人權法通過<br />\n我地自己唔係唔出力啲大國際戰線呀？"},{"pid":"6c32750e77abda98ded1d6ffd99a055fe8cadbdf","tid":1739621,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:20:23.000Z","msg":"[正視聽]重點唔係取唔取消區選，而係用咩理由取消<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1739653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1739653</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"638f535433675c77ae8e4eeee967470cadd631f5","tid":1739621,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:25:04.000Z","msg":"push"}]}